column2: "Me? I'm helping out another ARKS. It's a real drag, but he's the kind of guy you can't say no to."
"You've been trying really hard for someone who's just a rookie. I think people expect too much of you."
"Personally, I'm done trying to live up to unreasonable expectations. It can get you into serious trouble."
"If only I'd stuck to trying to help the people in front of me..."
"Old man Regius knows that about me, so why's he dragging me all the way out here? Is it some kind of test...?"
"Sorry, I got caught up in thought. Point is, don't let other people's expectations get the best of you. Alright, see you around."
